{"tid":289703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放工都落大雨？雷雨區未來一兩小時殺到","createTime":"2017-06-19T08:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T10:52:25.000Z","uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"675c6c673371f86f1d1c98ccbd4c8f31c407cc63","tid":289703,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"天文台下午3時45分發出特別天氣提示，指位於珠江口附近的一個雷雨區正逐漸從西面移近本港，並可能於未來一兩小時內影響香港。市民應提高警惕。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，一道低壓槽正為南海北部及廣東沿岸帶來驟雨及雷暴，預測本港下午和今晚大致多雲，有驟雨及幾陣狂風雷暴，初時雨勢有時頗大，展望未來一兩日天氣仍然不穩定及有驟雨，惟本周後期天氣炎熱，部分時間有陽光。"},{"pid":"bf35ad4ad5ba2a2a69d87494a45b88ec0660528e","tid":289703,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"已經落緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1ac6a64cabf94799beb272654139b3d92f8ed58","tid":289703,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"到撚左啦"},{"pid":"458d67eab1ff139be444e3ade4870fadf7e7b312","tid":289703,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170619/large/1497858656_d3f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170619%2Flarge%2F1497858656_d3f0.png&h=f39ea096&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"606ca6f49509c965fa2d933547e7be3a320a77fb","tid":289703,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:35:19.000Z","msg":"已經落緊喇屌"},{"pid":"951149108ebc719231e529e76ea2a0f5ee8751b9","tid":289703,"uid":102347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T08:36:58.000Z","msg":"又要比人屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmo